            "text": "On Wednesday, the Ninth Circuit Court of Appeals shot down an attempt by top oil firms to move a major climate lawsuit they’re facing to friendlier environs. Six California cities and counties had filed the suit to get the fossil fuel companies to pay for the cost of climate change. While the businesses had tried ",
